{"tid":1052631,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"（鬥摺）中興摺疊屏幕專利，對摺還可以露出","createTime":"2019-03-08T12:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T15:07:25.000Z","uid":50534,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5510bda38cd6777184960eb916a55cd0a709749","tid":1052631,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/03/08/zte-foldable-smartphone-is-a-clamshell-model/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F03%2F08%2Fzte-foldable-smartphone-is-a-clamshell-model%2F&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=af37ac71\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/03/08/zte-foldable-smartphone-is-a-clamshell-model/</a><br />\n中興摺疊屏幕專利，對摺還可以露出<br />\nBy Marco - 三月 8, 2019<br />\n近期，荷蘭網站 LetsGoDigital 爆料了中興申請的一項特殊的摺疊屏幕智能機專利。其實早在去年的 4月，中興就已經向世界知識產權局（WIPO）的全球設計數據庫，提交了這份外觀設計專利。直到現在才發布了草圖，可以看到中興至少設想了十幾種摺疊方案。<br />\n<br />\n大家還是否記得在 2017年10月的時候，中興給我們帶來了Axon M 摺疊智能機。但是因為當時柔性摺疊屏幕技術還未成熟，所以該機只是由兩塊獨立的屏幕構成。<br />\n<br />\n今年是摺疊屏幕和 5G 奮起的時代，技術成熟了中興也開始設想摺疊屏幕手機了。根據 LetsGoDigital 的爆料，該設計並不和華為會或者 Samsung 類似，而是類似翻蓋式的摺疊方式。<br />\n<br />\n1 of 3 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你展開手機的時候，並完全攤開的情況下，手機的邊框幾乎不可見。但是美中不足的地方在於為了保證結構的牢固，在手機的腰部留下了兩個明顯的鉸鏈凸起。影響了美觀。<br />\n<br />\n摺疊後會發現該設計並不是完全的對向摺疊，摺疊後後露出一部分屏幕，可以用來顯示信息等內容。目前，屏下鏡頭還不是成熟的方案，但是在該機上看不到前置鏡頭。還有一個奇怪的點在於沒有指紋傳感器，很可能是採用了側邊指紋解鎖的方式。在插圖中看到了手機右側有兩個按鍵，位於SIM 卡和存儲卡插槽的下方，底部為充電接口。不知道該設計會不會出現在現實生活中，目前還是保持等待的態度吧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/24234333242424243234.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F24234333242424243234.jpg&h=e0d593bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2342343342233424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F2342343342233424.jpg&h=99b5a6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3423532424323423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F3423532424323423.jpg&h=64267d25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cda71f0442f657f3eccc8b30ea213654b2845034","tid":1052631,"uid":28170,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"Game Boy Advance SP<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzOggCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzOggCG.jpg&h=17f02263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果無左個駁位其實都算係摺機中唔算既設計"},{"pid":"c2e70471f8aff979b4f90cb2d655ec1b02eb3834","tid":1052631,"uid":4394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"中間個駁位如果有野要禁點算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4a95d55af21e4db8143b456c362a62a651b6e9","tid":1052631,"uid":157312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"咁既長度有咩需要摺<br />\n摺埋啦中興"},{"pid":"5cf75d3173bc2d1b3f61e8bf13240cafc5774b4f","tid":1052631,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"依d摺唔哂既核突設計都仲夠膽拎去申請專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af6e4b83f97bf304a2ed4fa4f694ea22ad234d1","tid":1052631,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5cf75d3173bc2d1b3f61e8bf13240cafc5774b4f","tid":1052631,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"依d摺唔哂既核突設計都仲夠膽拎去申請專利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"擺明係申請哂先<br />\n博日後收過路費"},{"pid":"cf0c5c03a49c04b274b10efd7b4fdc7a35b27106","tid":1052631,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"下部可唔可以扭毛巾咁？"},{"pid":"3641729b80be854d370583c134ed7660beb7f93e","tid":1052631,"uid":158977,"like":0